00:21:42.301 --> 00:21:43.677
Aptal!

00:21:48.098 --> 00:21:51.185
Seni boğacağım!

00:21:51.185 --> 00:21:52.436
M-san!

00:21:56.690 --> 00:21:58.776
M-san!

